{
  "id": "adv_card_mei_02_03",
  "title": "早坂芽衣 3話 浜辺の散歩",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_summerfes-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "summerfes_beach_night",
      "startTime": null
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_02_03-mei001.m4a",
      "text": "ほらほら、{user}さーん！\nこっちこっちー！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hey‚ {user}!\nOver here!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 3.1666666666666665,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_02_03-mei002.m4a",
      "text": "ひゃーっ\n夜になるとさすがに冷えてくるねー",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hyaaah!\nOkay‚ it’s pretty cold at night.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 6.766666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_summerfes-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "summerfes_beach_night",
      "startTime": 10.5
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_02_03-mei003.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さん、ありがとね\n浜辺の散歩まで付き合ってくれて",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Thanks‚ {user}.\nFor taking this walk on the beach with me.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 13.566666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_02_03-mei004.m4a",
      "text": "ライブの余韻なのかな\nなんだか身体がむずむずしちゃうんだよね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I wonder if it’s because it’s after that big concert.\nI can’t seem to settle down.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 18.966666666666665,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_summerfes-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "summerfes_beach_night",
      "startTime": 22.3333333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_02_03-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "そういえば……今回の新曲は\n芽衣の意見で方向性が決まったらしいな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hey‚ about the new song‚\nI heard you decided on the direction for it?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 25.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_02_03-mei005.m4a",
      "text": "んー、そうなのかなー？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hmmm. I did?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 28.266666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_02_03-mei006.m4a",
      "text": "みんなで一杯話し合ったから\n芽衣がどうこうしたって感じしないんだけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We all talked about it a whole bunch‚\nso I don’t think it was just me.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 34.166666666666664,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_summerfes-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "summerfes_beach_night",
      "startTime": 37.6333333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_02_03-mei007.m4a",
      "text": "芽衣が曲作りに役立ったなら……\nちょっと嬉しいかも",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If I did help to make the new song‚\nthat makes me happy!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 40.56666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_summerfes-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "summerfes_beach_night",
      "startTime": 42.666666666666664
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_02_03-mei008.m4a",
      "text": "今回の新曲なんだけどさ\nすっごくいい歌になったけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That new song\nis really great‚ I love it.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 45.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_summerfes-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "summerfes_beach_night",
      "startTime": 48.4333333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_02_03-mei009.m4a",
      "text": "いい歌が出来たっていう結果だけじゃなくて\nその途中で得たものがいっぱいあったなって思うんだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But it’s not just about making a great song.\nI think I got a lot out of the experience too.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 51.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_summerfes-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "summerfes_beach_night",
      "startTime": 56.0666666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_02_03-mei010.m4a",
      "text": "みんなで意見をぶつけ合って\n悩んで、海で遊んで……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "All of our opinions bouncing off each other‚\nthinking so hard‚ then playing in the ocean.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 58.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_02_03-mei011.m4a",
      "text": "一曲が出来るまでに\nみんなとの絆がすっごく深まったなって",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Creating one new song\nreally brought us closer together.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 63.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_summerfes-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "summerfes_beach_night",
      "startTime": 67.6
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_02_03-mei012.m4a",
      "text": "だからかもしれないけど……\nステージがほんっっっとに楽しかったの！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That might be…\nwhy the concert was so much fun!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 70.63333333333334,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_summerfes-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "summerfes_beach_night",
      "startTime": 75.2666666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_summerfes-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "summerfes_beach_night",
      "startTime": 78
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_02_03-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "ん？　急に黙ってどうしたんだ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Huh? What’s with the sudden silent treatment?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 78,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_summerfes-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "summerfes_beach_night",
      "startTime": 81.63333333333334
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_02_03-mei013.m4a",
      "text": "今回の曲作りを通して\n改めて思ったんだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Making this new song made me\nreaffirm something important.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 83.96666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_02_03-mei014.m4a",
      "text": "芽衣は――アイドルとして\nもっともっと沢山の人を笑顔にしたい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I know what I want to do as an idol.\nMake as many people smile as I can!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 89.56666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_summerfes-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "summerfes_beach_night",
      "startTime": 92.56666666666666
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_02_03-mei015.m4a",
      "text": "今でも凄く楽しいよ？\nだけどね、まだまだ足りないって思ったんだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’m already having lots of fun‚ don’t get me wrong!\nBut there’s still something missing.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 95.56666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_summerfes-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "summerfes_beach_night",
      "startTime": 99.86666666666666
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_02_03-mei016.m4a",
      "text": "五人で頑張って\nいっぱいいっぱい頑張って",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I want the five of us to keep working hard.\nWorking so‚ so hard!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 101.96666666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_summerfes-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "summerfes_beach_night",
      "startTime": 109.7
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_02_03-mei017.m4a",
      "text": "それで……いつか月ストのみんなと\nアイドルの頂点に行きたい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "And one day‚ I want to take Moon Tempest\nto the pinnacle of the idol industry!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 109.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_02_03-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "（芽衣……こんな力強い表情をするようになったのか）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Mei… I’ve never seen her with such a powerful expression.）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 111.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_summerfes-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "summerfes_beach_night",
      "startTime": 117.06666666666666
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_02_03-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "芽衣はどうして……\nそこまで意志が強くなったんだ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I sense real conviction in you‚ Mei.\nWhere did you gain it from?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 119.06666666666666,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_02_03-mei018.m4a",
      "text": "へ、そんなに変わったかな？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Huh? Have I changed that much?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 121.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_summerfes-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "summerfes_beach_night",
      "startTime": 124.9
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_02_03-mei019.m4a",
      "text": "でも、{user}さんが言う通りに\nもし変わったとしたら……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But if you’re right‚ {user}.\nIf I have changed…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 128.23333333333332,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_02_03-mei020.m4a",
      "text": "ライブでも言ったけど\n芽衣が恋をしてるからかもね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It’s like I said during the concert.\nIt’s because I’m in love.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 133.13333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_summerfes-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "summerfes_beach_night",
      "startTime": 135.96666666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_02_03/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_02_03-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "もちろん聞いたよ\n月ストに……だろ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I heard you say that‚ yes.\nWith Moon Tempest‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 138.03333333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_summerfes-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "summerfes_beach_night",
      "startTime": 140.36666666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
